Title: Relates to third-party network contracts
Summary: Allows dental provider networks, certain health and hospital service corporations, and health care plans to enter into a third-party network contract to provide access to care services and discounted rates of a provider under a provider network contract.
LawCode: Add §§3217-k, 4242 & 4325-a, Ins L; add §4406-j, Pub Health L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the insurance law and the public health law, in relation to third-party network contracts
